{"tid":1990633,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"白票撚熱狗雲粉話投票冇用！班撚樣其實有咩高見呢？","createTime":"2020-04-27T00:10:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T11:27:12.000Z","uid":127575,"like":15,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b97a9e3cbc094a3dacf78177323e724b229dbc95","tid":1990633,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T00:10:14.000Z","msg":"淨係得把口話投票冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係又講唔出有咩高見有咩方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淨係識學白兵發夢FF美國軍隊救香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當香港人依家水深火熱再次相信民主派<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n國難當前熱狗分化撚白票撚淨係識得私怨行頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話投票冇用射落海唔益民主派區議會仲叫人投比保皇黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />乜撚嘢邏輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好彩香港人係好聰明！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後區議會民主派佔多數係眼睇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫人投保皇黨陳雲濕鳩呀伯收撚皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成場抗爭運動你地做過乜撚野呢？付出過D乜？<br />\n睇下人地民主黨老野胡志偉都勇過某位話市民係白痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成日連登出Post 搞分化<br />\n唔講以為 PR 課好多金 ！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最後提提大家盡快做選民登記<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就黎deadline <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好錯過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下載登記表<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4LeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=c4e762d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C</a>).pdf<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"cf5d6f08130af974ffe9cbf0a9a28f53e051e247","tid":1990633,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T00:14:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a77832949cdb9ccde785754a12f2cc9a701c23a2","tid":1990633,"uid":81562,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T00:17:41.000Z","msg":"投票冇用&gt;又派人出嚟選&gt;輸撚咗&gt;你班港豬唔投我唔配有民主"},{"pid":"aef239b11af3a3d7d8804aa1de0bca706e55a9d1","tid":1990633,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T00:17:44.000Z","msg":"班白票撚連太古手足都屌埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鬧哂全世界！<br />\n成日講失敗主義叫人放棄抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢地自己係度freeride咩撚都冇做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"707a5bae8ee82bdbc1b072dd5aabec1db187d0c9","tid":1990633,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aef239